(Last known, Archangle was standing in the hallway with Koj and 
Trinity.  Archangle had taken Trinity from the pod and taken her back 
to the Cybertron Fire.  He had her in the hallway and was telling her 
that he would help her find her parents. But her family was all 
killed in the ship crash, but Koj and Archangle don't know that for 
sure.  Koj just told her that her parents may still be alive and she 
is currently jumping around and all happy and stuff thinking that her 
family may still be alive.  But they would have to go tothe wreckage 
of the ship to know for sure.)
